The country dataset (`web/countries_data.js`) contains factual reference
material curated from public sources. Facts themselves are not copyrightable;
the curation, arrangement, prose summaries, and depth fields (history,
culture, religion, notable figures) are original work and protected.

Country flag emoji are part of the Unicode standard and are unrestricted.

Landmark image URLs reference images hosted on Wikimedia Commons under their
respective Creative Commons or public domain licences. These images are
referenced, not redistributed.

The Three.js library is licensed separately under the MIT licence and is
loaded at runtime from a CDN.

The NASA Blue Marble Earth texture is in the public domain (US Government work).

